    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of the African people of the same name living in the countries of Mali, Burkina Fasso, Côte d'Ivoire, Guinea, Sierra Leone, Gambia, Liberia, Guinea-Bissau, and Senegal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000044687/African Ethnonyms (1996)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Úsese para describir obras producidas por pueblos africanos del mismo nombre, que habitan los países de Mali, Burkina Faso, Costa de Marfil, Guinea, Sierra Leona, Gambia, Liberia, Guinea-Bissau y Senegal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Te gebruiken om werken te beschrijven van de gelijknamige Afrikaanse etnische groep die leeft in de landen Mali, Burkina Faso, Ivoorkust, Guinee, Sierra Leone, Gambia, Liberia, Guinee-Bissau en Senegal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用於描述居住在馬利（Mali）、布吉納法索（Burkina Faso）、象牙海岸、幾內亞、獅子山（Sierra Leone）、甘比亞、利比亞、幾內亞比索與塞內加爾等國家中同名的非洲種族所製造之作品。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
